ChangeLog for timeappend
===============================

Open SPRs:

Version 1.5 - 2002-05-13 (GV)
-----------
	+ Updated for param-2.0
	
Version 1.4 - 2001-07-24 (UL)
-----------
	+ temporarily disabled EPN related part of test harness because of
	  anomalies in testodf/scisimsimple data (see SPR 2128 for details)

Version 1.3 - 2001-01-09 (UL)
-----------
	+ trivial change to make optimizer happy

Version 1.2.3 - 2000-11-19 (GV)
-------------
	+ (src/testgti) add 63.xxx s to all reference times.

Version 1.2.2 - 2000-11-18 (GV)
-------------
	+ (src/timeappend.cc) toMet() -> toMET().

Version 1.2.1 - 2000-11-17 (GV)
-------------
	+ (src/timeappend.cc) change toUtc() to toMet().
	
Version 1.2 - 19-10-2000 (HS)
----------------------------
+ Fixed bug in OAL initialisation (SOC-SPR-1787).
+ INTERFACE CHANGE: Added new parameter node (SOC-SPR-1788).
	
Version 1.1 - 18-10-2000 (HS)
----------------------------
+ Fixed DEPEND problem (now depends on sas-1.234).

Version 1.0 - 17-10-2000 (HS)
----------------------------
+ Promoted v 0.16 to major version as task has been approved.
  (doc/timeappend_description.tex): Changed version number in doc accordingly.

Version 0.16 - 09-10-2000 (HS)
----------------------------
+ Re-delivered v 0.15.2 in M.m form
	
Version 0.15.2 - 21-06-2000 (HS)
----------------------------
+ (config/Makefile): Added .info file to Makefile (SOC-SPR-1534)
+ (test/testtimeappend): Converted script to Bourne-shell (SOC-SPR-1596).

Version 0.15.1 - 21-06-2000 (HS)
----------------------------
+ (test/testgti): Made tabgtigen calls more explicit (SOC-SPR-1585).

Version 0.15 - 25 May 2000 [HS]
----------------------------
+ Removed withodf and odf params from config (not used in code)
+ Removed params withinstrument and withdatamode, and added params
	withsettings and expnr. Updated doc accordingly.
+ added range to CCDID/QUADRANT columns for PN in doc.


Version 0.14 - 02 May 2000 [HS]
----------------------------
+ Now in line with testodf-0.42

Version 0.13 - 25 April 2000 [HS]
----------------------------
+ Now in line with testodf-0.41

Version 0.12 - 13 April 2000 [UL]
----------------------------
+ brought in line with oal-3.50

Version 0.11 - 31 Mar 2000 [HS]
----------------------------
+ Changed test harness to following name change of epauxexpand (now
	epauxcomb)

Version 0.10 - 29 Mar 2000 [HS]
----------------------------
+ Updated documentation based on comments from SSC.
	
Version 0.9 - 17 Mar 2000 [HS]
----------------------------
+ Fixed bug causing testgti to fail - pn.ds now has only one entry for frame 97.

Version 0.7 - 08 Mar 2000 [HS]
----------------------------
+ Defined SAS_ODF in testgti test harness.

Version 0.6 - 25 Feb 2000 [HS]
----------------------------
+ Fixed SOC-SPR 1206 : SAS_ODF not defined in test harness
	
Version 0.5 - 24 Feb 2000 [HS]
----------------------------
+ Fixed SOC-SPR 1139 : spurious parameters
+ Fixed SOC-SPR 1141 : should have parameter to specify 
	the name of the new column
+ Fixed SOC-SPR 1142 : wrong documentation for withdatamode 
	and datamode
+ Fixed SOC-SPR 1151 : parameter datamode not compatible with 
	contents of ODF

Version 0.4 - 21 Feb 2000 [HS]
----------------------------
+ Modified testgti test harness. Now in line with testodf-0.36


Version 0.3 - 27 Jan 2000 [HS]
----------------------------
+ Improved test harness (again) based on o/p of epauxexpand-0.2

Version 0.2 - 27 Jan 2000 [HS]
----------------------------
+ Improved test harness.

Version 0.1 - 26 Jan 2000 [HS]
----------------------------
+ Initial release.
